title: Raiders make Crosby NFL's highest-paid non-QB
description: DE Maxx Crosby has agreed to a three-year, $106.5 million extension with the Raiders that makes him the highest-paid non-QB in NFL history, sources told ESPN.
author: Ryan McFadden

title: Sources: Duke's Lucas signs deal to coach Miami
description: Duke associate head coach Jai Lucas has signed a deal to become the head men's basketball coach at Miami, sources told ESPN on Wednesday.
author: Jeff Borzello

title: 'Performance of my life' - Liverpool saved by 'best in world' Alisson
description: Alisson is described as "the best goalkeeper in the world" after his heroics help Liverpool produce a smash-and-grab performance to beat Paris St-Germain.

title: Elliott scores late winner as Liverpool claim 'smash & grab' win at PSG
description: Liverpool complete one of the biggest smash and grabs in Champions League history to come away from their last-16 first leg against Paris St-Germain with a win.

title: 2025 NFL Draft big board: The 50 best players in this class

title: 2025 NFL Draft scouting report: Donovan Jackson, OG/OT, Ohio State
description: Jackson was a big reason why the Buckeyes steamrolled defenses on the ground and his experience kicking out to tackle, and playing well, can only help him right now.

title: Jonas warns Price: I'm going to prove myself right
description: Natasha Jonas and Lauren Price went head to head at the final press conference ahead of their world championship unification fight at the Royal Albert Hall on Friday.

title: Paqueta betting hearing to begin this month as FA seeks lifetime ban
description: Lucas Paqueta's betting charge hearing is due to take place this month and will last three weeks, Sky Sports News understands.
